description:
Colgate Deep Clean Replaceable Brush Head refills, fits any Colgate ProClinical Electric Toothbrush. Made with soft thin-tipped bristles to sweep along the gumline, for healthier gums in 4 weeks*.

Colgate Deep Clean replacement toothbrush heads fits any Colgate ProClinical Electric Toothbrush.

The deep clean brush head refills has soft thin tipped bristles and designed for healthier gums in 4 weeks*.

The deep clean electric toothbrush replaceable head features:
- Compact head to clean back teeth
- Soft thin-tipped bristles sweep along gum line
- Power tip bristles clean hard-to-reach areas
- Tongue and cheek cleaner helps remove odour causing bacteria

Pack Includes: 2 x soft deep clean refill heads for Colgate Pro Clinical Electric Toothbrush

Dentists and hygienists recommended replacing your toothbrush refill every 3 months.

After use, rinse toothbrush head thoroughly, shake off excess water, and store upright.

*vs. a manual flat-trim toothbrush
